113
00:25:40.406 --> 00:25:42.942
Kerana manusia mereka
takkan bertahan sehari di planet ini.

114
00:25:43.042 --> 00:25:44.176
Kami mendapati...

115
00:25:50.917 --> 00:25:52.885
Dengar...

116
00:25:52.985 --> 00:25:56.155
