Setuju?

126
00:26:23.666 --> 00:26:26.000
Kau dah melihat Kalisk?

127
00:26:27.053 --> 00:26:31.123
Oh. ya. Aku dah melihat Kalisk.

128
00:26:42.902 --> 00:26:44.336
Baiklah.

129
